short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Call an api to fill the fields

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automate fields using our extension to progress through the webpages. It is currently used to fill the form internally for our applications. It is protected with username password also during login. This is simply to auto-fill the forms from the user's personal Google sheets when authenticated using Google account. No personal information is collected in any form using this.
